Cucumber - 
Acceptance criteria - 
DOR - Definition of ready - When scrum team gets the complete details about the user story and estimated it 
properly for taking up for the development

DOD - Definition of done - When development is done, testing is done, status of all test cases for this user story
is green and code is committed, then DOD is completed.

